description:
There’s always something we can do to help someone else. Agree? Helping others can be simple, but we often overcomplicate it. 

Watch this #short clip from “Family Network: Revival for Mission” with Elder Ted N. C. Wilson at https://youtu.be/SrDZruGGDk8.
